script::dom::bindings::trace

Trait script::dom::bindings::trace::JSTraceable[−][src]

pub unsafe trait JSTraceable {
    unsafe fn trace(&self, trc: *mut JSTracer);
}
Expand description

A trait to allow tracing (only) DOM objects.
